Russian 'lesbian couple' Irina Shumilova and Alyona Fursova have spoken out about their unique 'same sex' marriage in a country that bans such unions.

They were allowed to go ahead because Irina was born a man.

Asked why they wed, Irina said: 'In fact it is very simple. Why do people get married?'

